OL,10,FRead from quitting the scandal-hit     
OL,11,Forganisation.                          
OL,13,FHowever, the requests were refused,    
OL,14,FPost Office minister Kevin Hollinrake  
OL,15,Fsaid in response to an urgent question 
OL,16,Fin the House of Commons.               
OL,18,FIt comes as hundreds of sub-postmasters
OL,19,Fwait for compensation as the           
OL,20,Flong-running Horizon IT scandal        
OL,21,Fcontinues.                             
